The paper discusses the use of swarm intelligence (SI) and SI-based algorithms to solve optimization problems in science and engineering. This topic is closely related to several sub-categories of computer science, including neural networks and learning (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), systems and control (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.LG), and robotics (cs.RO). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
